":37820,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T05:32:51.000Z","msg":"Lawson呀yodobashi嗰啲都有得用<br />\n咪又係中國人用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咪又係用嚟走水貨用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}